title: Dream Offseason Moves | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
How to interpret the rumors and commentary of the NFL offseason (1:45), a brief look at Doug Baldwin’s career following his release in Seattle (13:15), and a list of dream offseason trades and acquisitions around the league (17:00).
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
